node.text: For @mjrodriguez7, landing the role of Blanca Evangelista in the FX drama #Pose isn't just a benchmark in her journey toward success — though it has absolutely highlighted the star's talent and charisma. It is also a platform for her to replace stereotypes and caricatures of transgender women with a complex portrayal of a hard-working mother-figure who happens to be transgender.
